::Aerotaur::
       He shrugs.  "I've been wrong before.  It happens.  Well... actually I 
can't remember before but I imagine that I've been wrong."  He sighs again.  
"I wish I had my memory back.  But I know what you mean about not wanting to 
be pinned down.  That individualistic streak runs strong in us my friend, 
very strong indeed."
